2)
fun_ptr is a pointer to function fun()
					// Defination
				--->	void fun(int a)
						{
						    printf("Value of a is %d\n", a);
						} 
					// Assignment
				--->	void (*fun_ptr)(int) = &fun;
					// Usage
				--->	(*fun_ptr)(10);

